## What to Test in Models

Test:
- ✅ Validations
- ✅ Associations
- ✅ Scopes
- ✅ Instance methods
- ✅ Class methods
- ✅ Callbacks

Don't test:
- ❌ Rails framework functionality
- ❌ Database operations (trust ActiveRecord)
- ❌ Private methods directly

